da criminali e' finita!


247
00:14:37.036 --> 00:14:37.737
Mel!

248
00:14:37.945 --> 00:14:39.914
Mel, tu sei con me, vero?

249
00:14:41.041 --> 00:14:41.892
Guarda.

250
00:14:42.285 --> 00:14:43.737
