- Dave! Jerry!


277
00:15:59.109 --> 00:16:02.269
Ottime notizie, ragazzi.
Siete stati promossi!


278
00:16:02.369 --> 00:16:04.197
Siete al comando, adesso, eh?

279
00:16:04.297 --> 00:16:05.592
Niente male!

280
00:16:14.600 --> 00:16:15.402
Cielo!

281
00:16:17.118 --> 00:16:21.219
